        <div>
          <div>
            <div>
              <p>
                Thank you for your interest in the Professional Mentor volunteer role! Please complete the following application by
                <b><%=@due_date%></b>.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>About Braven:</strong><br />
                The Braven Accelerator empowers promising young people on their path to college graduation, meaningful careers, and lives of impact. Alongside educational institutions, Braven provides a scalable model to discover, develop, and connect extraordinary, diverse, and driven young people to high-quality skill building, opportunities, and networks. Braven supports its Fellows by offering:</p>
                
              <ol>
                <li>The Braven Accelerator: a credit-bearing, semester-long career and leadership course</li>
                <li>Post-course programming that continues through college graduation</li>
              </ol>

              <p>
                An essential piece of this post-course programming is the Professional Mentors program. Professional Mentors (PMs) guide Braven Fellows on their path to securing quality postgraduate opportunities and support their professional development along the way. Each PM is paired with a senior or recent college graduate at <%= @program_site %> for <strong><%=@number_of_weeks%> weeks from <%=@kickoff_date%> - <%=@end_date%></strong> and provides weekly 1:1 coaching on the job or internship search and application process and professional competencies. The volunteer commitment is as follows:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Commit <b>~1.5 hrs per week</b> with option to continue meeting with Fellow after commitment ends</li>
                <li>Attend an <b>virtual</b> kickoff event on <b><%=@kickoff_date%></b></li>
                <li>Attend a <b>60 min</b> mid-commitment virtual check-in
                <li>Prepare for meetings and follow up as necessary throughout the week</li>
                <li>Guide Fellow through the steps of job attainment and help them develop professional polish</li>
                <li>Serve as an advocate and cheerleader for your Fellow</li>
                <li>Keep Braven staff updated on Fellow&#8217;s progress through weekly progress forms</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Questions: Email <a href="mailto:<%=@contact_email%>"><%=@contact_email%></a></p>
              <br />
              <div>
                <p>
                  <strong>We are looking for professionals who work in the following industries:</strong>
                  <br />
                </p>
                <p><%=simple_format(@desired_industries)%></p>
              </div>
